{"tid":109281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一路好走，魯芬","createTime":"2017-02-06T00:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T00:00:20.000Z","uid":15791,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96c72f7fa676bdcba2c878ddd8fe217dfca32a14","tid":109281,"uid":15791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:00:20.000Z","msg":"去年魯芬疑因在東莞拍網上電影期間，下榻酒店衛生欠佳致神經性皮炎，開頭以為只是普通皮膚痕癢，未有理會，後來才知是神經性皮炎，更暴瘦十多磅，且驗出肝酵素偏高。最終因皮肌炎導致肺部衰竭，於今日凌晨時分在家人朋友陪同下安詳離世，終年63歲。<br />\n<br />\n神經性皮炎發病主因是免疫系統失調所致，嚴重者波及身體其他器官，例如心臟、呼吸系統、食道及消化系統，亦可引起併發症如肺部纖維化發炎等。<br />\n<br />\n魯芬姪女接受傳媒訪問時承認，魯芬是因為免疫力差，致肺部受感染需住院，加上天氣轉寒，令其身體轉差，過農曆新年前已入院，豈料最終撒手人寰。<br />\n<br />\n魯芬最後一次更新fb，是上月29日中午三時，她貼上招牌可愛笑容，頭上紮了兩個兔仔耳高髻，相片應是去年拍狽年廣告的舊照，並留言道:「恭喜發財！雞年祝大家身體健康！龍馬精神！笑口常開！充滿正能量！！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/075749_0821e0ba7fde2078162487ef83b1a3b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F075749_0821e0ba7fde2078162487ef83b1a3b4.jpg&h=5b30c027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生無常，一切都好突然，永遠懷念你<br />\n我愛魯芬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}